
Setting up password:
>net user <Username> *
// will prompt you to set up password and confirm

Renaming UserName
> wmic useraccount where name='<OldUsername>' rename <NewUsername>


ADDING USERACCOUNT/DELETING ACCOUNT
>net user <username> <password> /ADD
>net user <username> /DEL

ADVANCE USERS OF NET USER COMMAND

To set fullname while creating the user account
>net user <username> <password> /ADD /FULLNAME:"User_Fullname"

ALLOW you TO Change password:

>net user <username> /ADD /PASSWORDCHG:Yes //if not allow will just change it to NO
